For the PCI Hot Plug DR option: All platform
              requirements of the base DR option architecture must be met (
              ).

For the PCI Hot Plug DR option: All OF requirements
              of the base DR option architecture must be met (
              ).

For the PCI Hot Plug DR option: All RTAS requirements
              of the base DR option architecture must be met (
              ).

For the PCI Hot Plug DR option: All OS requirements
              of the base DR option architecture must be met (
              ).

For the LRDR option: All platform requirements of the
